item.title: [HBASE-12888] Display number of regions on the table jsp page.
item.description: This is a simple patch to display the number of regions in the table jsp page in the info web page. Currently we have only the total number of regions in the regionserver. This adds the per table count of the regions.
item.summary: Display number of regions on the table jsp page.
